<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9d2814d-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s390h–15"><num value="390h–15">§ 390h–15.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated for fiscal years beginning after <date date="1992-09-30">September 30, 1992</date>, $4,000,000 to carry out the study authorized by <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s390h–14">section 390h–14 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc9d2814e-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/575/tXVI/s1633">Pub. L. 102–575, title XVI, § 1633</ref>, formerly § 1617, <date date="1992-10-30">Oct. 30, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/4669">106 Stat. 4669</ref>; renumbered § 1633 and amended <ref href="/us/pl/104/266/s2/a/1">Pub. L. 104–266, § 2(a)(1)</ref>, (b)(3), <date date="1996-10-09">Oct. 9, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3290">110 Stat. 3290</ref>, 3294.)</sourceCredit>
